-- Seven Seas Water Names Baldovino South America Operations Chief
-- B y   R a n d a l l   H a c k l e y
-- 2013-05-22T14:26:37Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-05-22/seven-seas-water-names-baldovino-south-america-operations-chief.html
Seven Seas Water Corp., a Tampa,
Florida-based water company that operates in the Caribbean and
Latin America, named Claudio Baldovino as president of its South
American operations and to the executive committee.  Baldovino, with 21 years in  investment banking , corporate
finance and asset management including as a partner and director
of private finance for Buena Vista Capital SA, will be based in
Santiago, Chile, Seven Seas said today in a statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Randall Hackley in London at 
